====================  Classes in HTML   ========================================
<h2 class="dark-orange"> Classes in Html</h2>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------




================= CSS Stylesheet  ==============================================

*** Class selector ***
.dark-orange {   		//    .	<--- the dot operator selects the "class"
	color: darkorange;
}
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

*** ID selector ***
#							<--- selects the "id" tags
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

*** h2 selector ***
h2 {						<--- selects all the h2 elements
	font-family: sans-serif;

}
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

===================================================================================================================================================================================================================================================

-------------------------- Selectors -----------------------------------------


selector {					// <--- the whole thing is called a "CSS rule"
							// <---
	property: value;		// <---
}							// <---



selector {	

	border: 		// adds border							
	background: 	// changes background 
	font-family:	// changes font style
	font-size: 		// changes font size
	color: 			// font color;
		
	
}

----------------------------- Direct decendant selector -----------------------


selectorParent>directChild{
	property: value;
}

main>p{
	background: purple;
}



-------------------------------- Decendant Selector ---------------------------


main p{
	background: purple;
}





-------------------------------- Combining Selectors -------------------------
//if you want to select a class and element 

p.comic{
	font-family: 'comic sans';
	color: red;
}


-------------------------------- Pseudo Classes -------------------------

a:link{
	font-size: 10px;		// all these are link realted , behaviors that 								// happen
}

a:active

a:hover

a:visited


--------------------------------  -------------------------













